candidates.body:
Bumps [syn](https://github.com/dtolnay/syn) from 1.0.18 to 1.0.19.
Release notes

Sourced from syn's releases.

1.0.19

  • Parse a more lenient extern type syntax inside extern blocks (#763)

  • e98f372 Parse ForeignItem type with generics and bounds

  • d290269 Update build status badge to GitHub Actions
  • 562ce7b Remove Travis configuration
  • 3e1ba83 Abbreviate clippy toolchain installation

  • 0bc5df7 Tweak os declaration in ci.yml

(yanked)
